{
  "title": "kuberag SLO",
  "uid": "kuberag-slo",
  "tags": ["kuberag", "slo", "rag"],
  "refresh": "30s",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Ingestion Freshness",
      "type": "gauge",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 12, "h": 8},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 3600},
              {"color": "red", "value": 86400}
            ]
          },
          "min": 0
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "time() - max(rag_knowledgebase_ingestions_total{result=\"succeeded\"}) by (namespace)",
          "refId": "A",
          "format": "time_series"
        }
      ],
      "options": {"showThresholdLabels": true, "showThresholdMarkers": true}
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Recall Percentiles",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"x": 12, "y": 0, "w": 12, "h": 8},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "custom": {"lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10}
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.5, sum(rate(rag_knowledgebase_recall_percent[5m])) by (le, namespace))",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "p50 - {{namespace}}"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(rag_knowledgebase_recall_percent[5m])) by (le, namespace))",
          "refId": "B",
          "legendFormat": "p95 - {{namespace}}"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(rag_knowledgebase_recall_percent[5m])) by (le, namespace))",
          "refId": "C",
          "legendFormat": "p99 - {{namespace}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom"}
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Retriever Latency",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 8, "w": 12, "h": 6},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# Retriever Latency\n\nRetriever latency metrics are not yet instrumented in the retriever server.\n\nPlanned metrics:\n- `rag_retriever_query_duration_seconds` (histogram)\n- `rag_retriever_query_total` (counter)\n\nTrack [issue #TODO](https://github.com/furkandogmus/kuberag/issues) for progress."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Ingestion Error Rate",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"x": 12, "y": 8, "w": 12, "h": 6},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "red", "value": 0.05}
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(rag_knowledgebase_ingestions_total{result=\"failed\"}[5m]) / rate(rag_knowledgebase_ingestions_total[5m])",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "{{namespace}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Auto-tune Duration p95",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 14, "w": 24, "h": 8},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {"lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10}
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, rate(rag_knowledgebase_autotune_duration_seconds_bucket[30m]))",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "p95"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom"}
      }
    }
  ]
}
